{
  "stem": "9943.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember my father came home, and he was singing 'The Marseillaise'-- 'The Marseillaise,' this French--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--French song because he was a liberal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was happy with the fact that there was a revolution at the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember, at home-- oh yeah, and I had a Hebrew teacher that came home to teach me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I continued with Hebrew that I started in the shtetl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I continued in home quite solidly, to translate from Hebrew to Russian and from Russian to Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my father was playing chess with that Hebrew teacher.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember I-- one day-- didn't want to do the lesson because-- and my father had a look at the book.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he decided that, that it's too difficult for me, what the teacher wanted me to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the teacher said that he, he knew what he was telling me to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I can do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it ended up that for a while, I didn't have these Hebrew lessons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they stopped playing chess.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one nice day, I decided I'll translate what the teacher was wanting-- wanted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Took the book, translated it, and then they became-- they got reconciled with each other, my teacher with my father.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But for a while, I didn't have to have those Hebrew lessons, because I didn't-- I was not going to do that, that assignment.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I could-- I could tell you a lot of things about this period between [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this 1917 and 1922, when we went back home.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Home, I mean, where we were-- where I was born.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And first came to, to-- to Rostov, came the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then there was the fight",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
